Materials and methods 99 children, 6-17 years, F 44 and M 55, suffering from Primary Headaches and admitted to Headache Center in the years 2016- 2017 are the sample. 7 patients were excluded because they did not adhere to the study due to lack of therapeutic compliance and because they did not return to clinical controls. The patients referred to the Headache center are selected consecutively. The open-label study evaluating clinical trial concerns the evaluation of the following parameters: headache diagnosis (ICHD-III,2013), migraine index: \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
